    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Yay! Your courier is on their way!</h2></strong><br><br>A game about a delivery guy trying to complete his order, but luck is certainly not on his side. You're playing as a pure evil with a degree in ruining delivery guy's life, and with each try it is becoming even stronger at it. Placing traps, misleading poor souls, basically, you are the reason why people get their deliveries in an awful condition, if they get them at all.<br><br>With each new try you will unlock more villainous pranks, but couriers also do become tougher. The better we do at stopping them, the higher are the losses of the courier company, and that's our main goal!<br><br>For any feedback, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:m83galaxyteam@gmail.com\">m83galaxyteam@gmail.com</a><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839900/extras/19d56c0b8f2315f988f8ae03e722b83b.poster.avif?t=1653588156\" width=320 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839900/extras/19d56c0b8f2315f988f8ae03e722b83b.webm?t=1653588156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1839900/extras/19d56c0b8f2315f988f8ae03e722b83b.mp4?t=1653588156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
